# Flakes8

## Project Page
http://flake8.pycqa.org/en/latest/index.html#quickstart

## Installation
It can be installed with:
pip install --upgrade flake8

## Test a file
flake8 path/to/code/to/check.py
# or
flake8 path/to/code/

## rcfile 
flake8 crummy_code.py --config=.flakerc

